xediaRadiusMIB.name: xediaRadiusMIB
xediaRadiusMIB.description: This module defines additional objects for management of Radius in Xedia devices, above and beyond what is defined in the proposed drafts.

xradiuscAdminAuthStatus.name: xradiuscAdminAuthStatus
xradiuscAdminAuthStatus.description: The administrative status of Radius Authentication in the router. Changing this parameter may require a node boot to take affect.

xradiuscAdminActgStatus.name: xradiuscAdminActgStatus
xradiuscAdminActgStatus.description: The administrative status of Radius Accounting in the router. Changing this parameter may require a node boot to take affect.

xradiuscDebugCmd.name: xradiuscDebugCmd
xradiuscDebugCmd.description: The control for dumping in/out radius packets, and error/trace messages to the console. Although the summary of commands is displayed when read, command modifications must be done one at a time.

xradiuscNasId.name: xradiuscNasId
xradiuscNasId.description: The NAS ID assigned to this node.

xradiuscNasIP.name: xradiuscNasIP
xradiuscNasIP.description: The NAS IP Address assigned to this node.

xradiuscBackgroundTimer.name: xradiuscBackgroundTimer
xradiuscBackgroundTimer.description: The number of seconds inwhich the background task will perform cleanup.

xradiuscMaxOutstanding.name: xradiuscMaxOutstanding
xradiuscMaxOutstanding.description: The maximum number of outstanding resquests.

xradiuscOperAuthStatus.name: xradiuscOperAuthStatus
xradiuscOperAuthStatus.description: The ccurrent operational state of Radius Authentication on the router.

xradiuscOperActgStatus.name: xradiuscOperActgStatus
xradiuscOperActgStatus.description: The ccurrent operational state of Radius Accounting on the router.

xradiuscOperNasId.name: xradiuscOperNasId
xradiuscOperNasId.description: The NAS ID assigned to this node.

xradiuscOperNasIP.name: xradiuscOperNasIP
xradiuscOperNasIP.description: The NAS IP Address currently being used.

xradiuscOperGenErrors.name: xradiuscOperGenErrors
xradiuscOperGenErrors.description: The number of general errors encounted by the Radius Client Task.

xradiuscOperAuthQCurr.name: xradiuscOperAuthQCurr
xradiuscOperAuthQCurr.description: The current number of elements in the Authentication queue.

xradiuscOperAuthQMax.name: xradiuscOperAuthQMax
xradiuscOperAuthQMax.description: The maximum number of elements in the Authentication queue at one time.

xradiuscOperAuthExpected.name: xradiuscOperAuthExpected
xradiuscOperAuthExpected.description: The expected number of elements in the Authentication queue by monitoring the enqueue/dequeue operations.

xradiuscOperAuthEnqueued.name: xradiuscOperAuthEnqueued
xradiuscOperAuthEnqueued.description: The number of requested posted to the Authentication queue.

xradiuscOperAuthDequeued.name: xradiuscOperAuthDequeued
xradiuscOperAuthDequeued.description: The number of requested removed from the Authentication queue.

xradiuscOperActgQCurr.name: xradiuscOperActgQCurr
xradiuscOperActgQCurr.description: The current number of elements in the Accounting queue.

xradiuscOperActgQMax.name: xradiuscOperActgQMax
xradiuscOperActgQMax.description: The maximum number of elements in the Accounting queue at one time.

xradiuscOperActgExpected.name: xradiuscOperActgExpected
xradiuscOperActgExpected.description: The expected number of elements in the Accounting queue by monitoring the enqueue/dequeue operations.

xradiuscOperActgEnqueued.name: xradiuscOperActgEnqueued
xradiuscOperActgEnqueued.description: The number of requested posted to the Accounting queue.

xradiuscOperActgDequeued.name: xradiuscOperActgDequeued
xradiuscOperActgDequeued.description: The number of requested removed from the Accounting queue.

xradiuscOperPendingListCurr.name: xradiuscOperPendingListCurr
xradiuscOperPendingListCurr.description: The current number of Authentication and Accounting requests Pending.

xradiuscOperPendingListMax.name: xradiuscOperPendingListMax
xradiuscOperPendingListMax.description: The maximum number of Authentication and Accounting requests Pending at one time.

xradiuscOperPendingExpected.name: xradiuscOperPendingExpected
xradiuscOperPendingExpected.description: The expected number of elements in the Pending list by monitoring the enqueue/dequeue operations.

xradiuscOperPendingEnqueued.name: xradiuscOperPendingEnqueued
xradiuscOperPendingEnqueued.description: The number of requested posted to the Pending list.

xradiuscOperPendingDequeued.name: xradiuscOperPendingDequeued
xradiuscOperPendingDequeued.description: The number of requested removed from the Pending list.

xradiuscOperLastPktID.name: xradiuscOperLastPktID
xradiuscOperLastPktID.description: The last Packet ID that was used.

xradiuscOperNextPktID.name: xradiuscOperNextPktID
xradiuscOperNextPktID.description: The next Packet ID that will most likely be used.

xradiuscOperLastAuthIndex.name: xradiuscOperLastAuthIndex
xradiuscOperLastAuthIndex.description: The index of the last authentication server used.

xradiuscOperLastActgIndex.name: xradiuscOperLastActgIndex
xradiuscOperLastActgIndex.description: The index of the last accounting server used.

xRadiuscAuthSvrTable.name: xRadiuscAuthSvrTable
xRadiuscAuthSvrTable.description: A list of Radius Client Authentication Server entries.

xRadiuscAuthSvrEntry.name: xRadiuscAuthSvrEntry
xRadiuscAuthSvrEntry.description: An entry containing additional management information applicable to a particular Radius Client Authentication Server.

xradiuscAuthSvrIpAddress.name: xradiuscAuthSvrIpAddress
xradiuscAuthSvrIpAddress.description: The IP Address of the specified Authentication Server. If this address is configured, it is used exclusively to communicate with this server.

xradiuscAuthSvrName.name: xradiuscAuthSvrName
xradiuscAuthSvrName.description: The name identifying the specified Authentication Server. If no IP Address is configured, then this name MAY be used during a DNS lookup.

xradiuscAuthSvrPort.name: xradiuscAuthSvrPort
xradiuscAuthSvrPort.description: The udp port number that the specified Authentication Server is listening for requests.

xradiuscAuthSvrTimeout.name: xradiuscAuthSvrTimeout
xradiuscAuthSvrTimeout.description: The number of seconds to wait for a response to a resquests.

xradiuscAuthSvrRetries.name: xradiuscAuthSvrRetries
xradiuscAuthSvrRetries.description: The number of times to resend the server a requests when no response has been received.

xradiuscAuthSvrPriority.name: xradiuscAuthSvrPriority
xradiuscAuthSvrPriority.description: The priority assigned to this server. Lowest priority servers are used first. In the case of multiple servers having the same priority, they will be used in a round- robin fashion when their priority is the highest of the available servers.

xradiuscAuthSvrSecretKey.name: xradiuscAuthSvrSecretKey
xradiuscAuthSvrSecretKey.description: The shared secret key associated with the specified server. It is used to 'hide' user passwords and authenticate requests and responses. When this object is read from a non-superuser, '--------' is returned in order to maintain security.

xradiuscAuthSvrVendorOffset.name: xradiuscAuthSvrVendorOffset
xradiuscAuthSvrVendorOffset.description: The offset used to assign Vendor Specific attribute IDs to the standard attribute number space. Setting this value to 0, forces the encoding of Vendor Specific attributes within the Vendor's number space, using the standard 'Vendor-Specific' attribute. Setting this to a non-zero value uses standard attribute encoding, with the Vendor Specific Base for the attributes beginning with this offset.

xradiuscAuthSvrOperIpAddress.name: xradiuscAuthSvrOperIpAddress
xradiuscAuthSvrOperIpAddress.description: The IP Address currently being used to communicate the specified Authentication server.

xradiuscAuthSvrOperState.name: xradiuscAuthSvrOperState
xradiuscAuthSvrOperState.description: The operational state of the specified Authentication server. The 'unknown' state will be set periodically to allow 'notResponding' servers to be retried after a period of time.

xradiuscAuthSvrOperStateChange.name: xradiuscAuthSvrOperStateChange
xradiuscAuthSvrOperStateChange.description: The value of sysUpTime when the Authentication server last changed state.

xradiuscAuthSvrOperBadPktIds.name: xradiuscAuthSvrOperBadPktIds
xradiuscAuthSvrOperBadPktIds.description: The count of unexpected Packet IDs received on this port.

xradiuscAuthSvrOperRxErrors.name: xradiuscAuthSvrOperRxErrors
xradiuscAuthSvrOperRxErrors.description: The count of general Receive errors encountered by this server

xradiuscAuthSvrOperTxErrors.name: xradiuscAuthSvrOperTxErrors
xradiuscAuthSvrOperTxErrors.description: The count of general Transmit errors encountered by this server

xradiuscAuthSvrRowStatus.name: xradiuscAuthSvrRowStatus
xradiuscAuthSvrRowStatus.description: This variable displays the status of the entry. Setting it to 'destroy' marks the entry as removed. Eventually, when no other applications depend on that particular resource, it will be completely removed from the table. Setting it to either 'create', or 'active' will add a row to the table.

xRadiuscActgSvrTable.name: xRadiuscActgSvrTable
xRadiuscActgSvrTable.description: A list of Radius Client Accounting Server entries.

xRadiuscActgSvrEntry.name: xRadiuscActgSvrEntry

xradiuscActgSvrIpAddress.name: xradiuscActgSvrIpAddress

xradiuscActgSvrRetries.name: xradiuscActgSvrRetries
xradiuscActgSvrRetries.description: The number of times to resend the server a requests when no response has been received.

xradiuscActgSvrPriority.name: xradiuscActgSvrPriority
xradiuscActgSvrPriority.description: The priority assigned to this server. Lowest priority servers are used first. In the case of multiple servers having the same priority, they will be used in a round- robin fashion when their priority is the highest of the available servers.

xradiuscActgSvrSecretKey.name: xradiuscActgSvrSecretKey
xradiuscActgSvrSecretKey.description: The shared secret key associated with the specified server. It is used to authenticate requests and responses. When this object is read from a non-superuser, '--------' is returned in order to maintain security.

xradiuscActgSvrVendorOffset.name: xradiuscActgSvrVendorOffset

xradiuscActgSvrOperState.name: xradiuscActgSvrOperState
xradiuscActgSvrOperState.description: The operational state of the specified Accounting server. The 'unknown' state will be set periodically to allow 'notResponding' servers to be retried after a period of time.

xradiuscActgSvrOperStateChange.description: The value of sysUpTime when the Accounting server last changed state.

xradiuscActgSvrOperBadPktIds.description: The count of unexpected Packet IDs received on this port.

xradiuscActgSvrOperRxErrors.name: xradiuscActgSvrOperRxErrors
xradiuscActgSvrOperRxErrors.description: The count of general Receive errors encountered by this server

xradiusCompliance.name: xradiusCompliance
xradiusCompliance.description: The compliance statement for all agents that support this MIB. A compliant agent implements all objects defined in this MIB.

xradiusAllGroup.description: The set of all accessible objects in this MIB.
